title: Killers Amongst Us: Real Life "Hell's Kitchen," Gorgeous Restauranteur Disappears. What happened to Dawn? (part 5)
itunes:title: Killers Amongst Us: Real Life "Hell's Kitchen," Gorgeous Restauranteur Disappears. What happened to Dawn? (part 5)
description:
After incriminating comments are make by David Viens' daughter that he was behind the supposed text from missing Dawn Viens, saying she was starting a new life, Viens becomes the prime suspect. When confronted by detectives, Viens and his story about Dawn's disappearance falls apart.
